{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[C]When the Master [C7]speaks the heavens [F]open wide
When He [C]waves His mighty [Am]hand the stormy [D7]seas sub[G7]side
When He [C]smiles at His [C7]children it's like a [F]bright shining light
When He [C]walks into your heart [F]peace and [C]love [G7]abi[C]des
{end_of_verse}

